<h1 id="panel">Panel</h1>
<p>Presents content by sliding over the rest of the application, which is covered by a partially-transparent overlay. Best used for experiences that do not require explicit context for heavy-weight creation/edit/management tasks such as settings, multi-field
    forms, and permissions. For containers used for complex tasks that requires context, use a separate Pane alongside the existing experience such as a List/Details layout.</p>
